    <h1>Our Mission</h1>
    <p>For more than 40 years, Byers Engineering Company's mission has been to provide high-quality technical services and software solutions to the communications, utility, and government industries and, in doing so, to earn the highest respect possible for the firm from our clients, suppliers, and employees. </p>
    <p class="worx">This commitment is implicit in the company logo, three sine waves representing forward movement, both scientifically and sociologically. </p>
